{"tid":1593714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兩個南亞人推閘，foodpanda無理","createTime":"2019-09-25T07:58:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T08:32:51.000Z","uid":320211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c8dd94fcc65a8c4c3ec97d84b96c9820b52b0a6a","tid":1593714,"uid":320211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:58:20.000Z","msg":"1545<br />\n啱啱係尖沙嘴地鐵站聽到有兩個南亞裔男人好大聲講野，我就望左過去。<br />\n其中一個邊講野邊推閘之後，對住第二個男人大叫兼做推閘手勢，教佢點推閘。<br />\n兩個都推閘入左地鐵站，推閘個聲好響，佢哋又好大聲講嘢，foodpanda一早留意到，全程望住，但聲都冇出過，冇捉。<br />\n淨係捉香港人<br />\n淨係捉後生<br />\n🖕🏻🖕🏻🖕🏻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YXsYBr7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYXsYBr7.jpg&h=145fb216&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KLShR0t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKLShR0t.jpg&h=6630a6d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"417e8e7d8ff4ec39c79722f14fbe6c6429587976","tid":1593714,"uid":11798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:32:51.000Z","msg":"唔俾係自己人去黨鐵逗糧？<br />\n利申 我跳開果個站望見都無理"}]}